# Building on Base: From 0 to 100 Commits

## What I built
Over the past few weeks I built a full on-chain ecosystem on Base:
- An ERC-20 token (BHNK)
- An NFT collection (BhanksNFT)
- A DeFi staking protocol
- A DAO governance system
- A Next.js frontend connecting it all

## What I learned
- How Solidity smart contracts work
- How wagmi and viem connect wallets to React
- How to deploy to Base Sepolia and Base mainnet
- How to verify contracts on Basescan
- The importance of testing before deploying

## What's next
- Gasless minting with Coinbase Paymaster
- IPFS metadata for NFTs
- Growing the BHNK community

